Description: Container-based development environment manager
 Enclave provides isolated container environments for AI coding assistants
 and development tools. It manages Docker containers with network isolation,
 authentication injection, and tool-specific configurations.
 .
 Supported tools include Claude, Codex, Gemini, OpenCode, and more.
